name: demographics
description: Customer demographic information such as age, marital status, education. This table is updated every 6 weeks and is source from a third-party data provider

name: campaign_info
description: Campaign summary information, how often and when a customer has been contact and the outcome of contact. This table is updated every time a customer is contacted and when conversion is triggered.

name: mktg_model_v1
description: Summary features for the marketing model v1, these features are being served online at customer_id and campaign id level
